this is a simple crawler system on linux
	./bin/  contains the manipulators of the system, may be binaries or scripts 
	./conf/ contains the config files
	./src/  contains the source codes 
you may need to add the following documents for running 
	./data/pagebase/
	./data/linkbase/
	./tmp/
	./log/
for more config infomations, check the files under ./conf/
